channel.description:
Very basic, just needed it for a question so I did it quick lol...
[php]
<?php
	$breads = array("Rye", "Wheat", "Italian");
	$meats = array("Turkey", "Ham", "Bologna");
	$cheeses = array("American", "Swiss");
	$i = 0;

	foreach($breads as $bread) {
		foreach($meats as $meat) {
			foreach($cheeses as $cheese) {
				$i++;
				echo($bread.'->'.$meat.'->'.$cheese.'<br>');
			}
		}
	}
	echo('Total Choices: '.$i);
?>
[/php]

It should be easy for anyone to simply edit it so it can be used for any situation, etc etc...
